cs.DL, cs.DB, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.CE 

This paper discusses the need for a sophisticated categorization environment for scientific codes and datasets, which falls under the domain of digital libraries (cs.DL) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of metadata to enhance searchability and collaboration, which is relevant to information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of Fluidinfo, a social metadata engine, is also discussed, which falls under the domain of software engineering (cs.SE) and computer engineering (cs.CE).
